CustomSettingValue.UserfriendlyName:
Enabled - Hide float color extensions (GL_ARB_color_buffer_float;
                        GLX_ARB_fbconfig_float for X11/GLX; WGL_ARB_pixel_format_float for Windows/WGL) if GPU resorts
                        to software fallback possible due to lack of two-sided lighting support (only on NV4x/G7x)
